ies provide constraints on both star formation and subsequent dynamical\nevolution. The low frequency of true physical companions at separations $>\\!5\"$\nis confirmed by examination of the subset of the nearest Cepheids and also the\ndensity of the fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 19:42:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
