 phase estimation protocol is a simple maximal-information gain\nstrategy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 20:30:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 May 2016 16:02:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2016 11:12:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 07:47:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-11"}
