 where most chaotic\norbits are found and it is the only region where chaotic orbits outnumber\nregular orbits, in the early evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 21:09:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2016 13:40:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-08"}
