cavities is also proposed.\nRealistic considerations on experimental realizations reveal advantages of\ntransition metal dichalcogenide monolayer quantum-dots over conventional\nsemiconductor quantum-emitters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2016 06:46:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2017 22:19:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2017 23:08:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
